    "DisplayTitle": "Orange Lvl. Contract: Protect Fuel Tanks",
    "Description": "One of our high priority clients is under attack from a criminal gang targeting their <EM4>~mission(Objects)</EM4> in <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>. The client\u2019s assets are valuable, so we need to keep those safe at all costs, but I won\u2019t kid \u2013 it\u2019ll be a challenge and a half with these thugs determined to do some real damage. \n\nIf it were me, I wouldn\u2019t hesitate to <EM>bring backup</EM4> to deal with them. They\u2019re no joke, so we\u2019re offering a well-earned <EM4>~mission(ScripAmount) MG Scrip</EM4> to the main contractor who deals with these guys successfully. \n\nBest of luck,\n\nKevin Walton\nDispatcher, Foxwell Enforcement\n'Security, Your Way'\n\nFoxwell Enforcement is a bonded security specialist licensed to operate throughout the UEE. We are always looking for new operators to join our family. If you or anyone you know is interested, please reach out to one of our contract representatives.",
    "DescriptionKey": "Foxwell_DefendDestructibleEntites_H_Desc_001",
    "DisplayDescription": "One of our high priority clients is under attack from a criminal gang targeting their <EM4>Fuel Tanks</EM4> in <EM4>Asteroid Mining Base</EM4>. The client\u2019s assets are valuable, so we need to keep those safe at all costs, but I won\u2019t kid \u2013 it\u2019ll be a challenge and a half with these thugs determined to do some real damage. \n\nIf it were me, I wouldn\u2019t hesitate to <EM>bring backup</EM4> to deal with them. They\u2019re no joke, so we\u2019re offering a well-earned <EM4>[ScripAmount] MG Scrip</EM4> to the main contractor who deals with these guys successfully. \n\nBest of luck,\n\nKevin Walton\nDispatcher, Foxwell Enforcement\n'Security, Your Way'\n\nFoxwell Enforcement is a bonded security specialist licensed to operate throughout the UEE. We are always looking for new operators to join our family. If you or anyone you know is interested, please reach out to one of our contract representatives.",
